BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 684.00 Td (statistically significant, which suggests the TMR-related difference was similar across sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 668.00 Td (conditions in this sample. These conclusions are limited to the provided synthetic dataset and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 652.00 Td (should be interpreted as exercise outcomes rather than confirmatory evidence from a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.00 636.00 Td (preregistered study.) Tj ET
